[There is a correction of this report: Measles update (13): corr 20200428.7273471
The moderator comments in item [4] below, mistakenly include misleading and incorrect information from The National Vaccine Information Center (NVIC) about the efficacy of the MMR vaccine. Scientifically accurate information backed by data in the ACIP (Advisory Committee on Immunization Practices) on recommendations about the efficacy of the MMR vaccine is available at https://www.cdc.gov/vaccines/vpd/mmr/public/index.html). - Mod.LK]

